				\begin{document}$$r = 1 - \mathop {\sum}\limits_{k = 1}^K {\frac{{n_k}}{N}\left( {\frac{{o_k}}{{n_k}} - p_k} \right)^2}{.}$$\end{document}r=1-∑k=1KnkNoknk-pk2.The reliability is computed for the two observational datasets and then averaged to account for observational uncertainties.

